# =============================================================================
# Heavy artifacts (NOT pushed to GitHub)
#   outputs/checkpoints  ~ 188 GB (6 stems x 3 seeds x 5 folds best.pt)
#   outputs/cache        ~  2 MB cached per-view OOF tensors
# =============================================================================
outputs/
checkpoints/
*.pt
*.bin
*.safetensors
*.ckpt

# Cached intermediate matrices
.cache/
*.npz
*.parquet
*.pkl

# =============================================================================
# Runtime logs (regenerable)
# =============================================================================
logs/
*.log
*.jsonl

# =============================================================================
# Data
#   The official 1,000-sample dataset (vpesg4k_train_1000 V1.csv / .json) at
#   repo root IS tracked because the competition organiser releases it publicly.
#
#   Everything else inside data/ is local-only:
#     - data/raw/         (1.3 GB sustainability-report PDFs from public sources)
#     - data/processed/   (pseudo-label CSVs, U10 corpus, U6-pro back-translation)
#     - data/splits/      (per-stem K-Fold index files; regenerable from seeds)
# =============================================================================
data/

# =============================================================================
# Reports — keep only EDA images + final analysis markdown.
# Everything else is per-run experiment dumps that bloat the repo.
# =============================================================================
reports/logs/
reports/runs/
reports/experiments/
reports/analysis/
reports/u6/
reports/eda/*.html

# =============================================================================
# Submissions / scratch
# =============================================================================
outputs/submissions/
scratch/
*.bak
*.bak.md
TODO.local.md

# =============================================================================
# Scraping intermediates (HTML probes from MOPS / sustainability portals)
# =============================================================================
scripts/_mops_pages/
scripts/_mops_probe2/
scripts/_*_probe*/
scripts/_*_pages/
